This Product Council heard a report from the Platform Quality and Security workstream, which included a review of the overall activities of the workstream, and a presentation of the substantial progress made in creating a Software Bill of Materials (SBOM) for the Mojaloop platform, and the value that offers in ensuring both the quality and the security of Mojaloop.
The session was led by Sam Kummary, who leads the WS, and Shuchita Prakash, who was instrumental in creating the SBOM.

The recording of the session is at https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=iNmYBVeiXLQ
